high_descs: Turn around to face the white stove.
Pick the pan up from the back left burner.
Bring the pan with you and move to face the kitchen sink.
Put the pan in the sink and wash it, then get it out of the sink again.
Bring the pan with you and move back to face the stove.
Put the pan down on the back right burner on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and take two steps, then turn left and face the stove.
Pick up the pan that is on the burner in the back left corner of the stove.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the pan in the sink, then turn on the water for three seconds, then turn the water off and pick up the pan.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Put the pan down behind the other pan on the stove.
Turn around and face the stove on the left.
Pick up the pan on the left rear burner from the stove.
Carry the pan and turn around and move toward the fridge. Turn left to face the sink.
Place the pan in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the pan.
Hold the pan and turn to the left to move back to the stove.
Place the pan on the stove, on the back right burner.
anns.task_desc: Clean a pan and move it to the stove.
